{"tid":252204,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以說服屋企人一齊養汪汪","createTime":"2017-05-21T14:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T02:09:57.000Z","uid":99359,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a32465b54552a553ad4c7645d5e4961d546604da","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"除左媽咪怕污糟之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他家人都中意汪<br />\n我媽咪應該有少少潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cec4d4aedd761e1bca580f05ddb1e5a06e79db","tid":252204,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多"},{"pid":"6fab076699d73d22787a4819009d503a9659205c","tid":252204,"uid":106087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n唔好啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔一定得  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果樓豬媽媽堅決反對<br />\n最後都係害左隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3aa292bf0bd8cd18ba63d246e0eb8ab9f606674","tid":252204,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:16:22.000Z","msg":"比熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc813346cf9a895fa6378ee4fae80d79f103c72e","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n唔好啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔一定得  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果樓豬媽媽堅決反對<br />\n最後都係害左隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都咁話 所以說服左再肯定左先敢養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0304ccaa40f74524b5cdf08f443305e655df710c","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好可愛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb162a60051531c6dbab8f71a7fd8177a221e87e","tid":252204,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"趕你媽出街"},{"pid":"a7fa634565e3a03db3898ea6acb8e1510c56c832","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c642cc2063af7b524812b6d7814fa13be4cdd798","tid":252204,"uid":32976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"你係咪預左呢十幾年都陪佢先。<br />\n想清楚啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1045330b9520520bbae0ebe3de21f9205c2810","tid":252204,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得你呀媽反對都好正常<br />\n因為養狗真係會好麻煩同會好臭<br />\n如果你係可以自己全部負責晒關於養狗既野<br />\n包括每日既屎屎尿尿 帶佢出街 沖涼 餵佢食野<br />\n同埋如果你唔係屋企 EG去左旅行 咁你會放棄去旅行定交底隻狗比你屋企人湊??<br />\n老左可能會失禁 到時你可能每日返到屋企成地都係尿同屎<br />\n當然呢D例子可能係太極端 但真係要諗<br />\n<br />\n一個屋企養狗真係唔只係一個人既事 係會影響晒全屋企<br />\n如果你有信心養狗唔會影響到你家人 我相信佢地都唔會阻止"},{"pid":"f3854b74c5188a91f4ad366a9c944ba1a13a4708","tid":252204,"uid":109513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"老母唔鐘意狗真係唔好養，又多說話比你聽，又會瘋狂用漂白水拖地消毒（對狗唔好），會攪到家無寧日。（朋友個案）<br />\n<br />\n利申：老母最錫隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d385396b109245ad31936c6dc50e71849db1280","tid":252204,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n岩 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f871ec393087b88b1d4d81ace4cbf770987b9b5","tid":252204,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n岩 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係唔係你自己照顧哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係既真係好on 9"},{"pid":"54b1194ea0fafe5441abbbd10c40f023aa9d0f2c","tid":252204,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n岩 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係唔係你自己照顧哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係既真係好on 9</blockquote><br />\n打針 糧 用品都係我自己搞掂<br />\n我係屋企就我照顧<br />\n我唔係度就我啊媽睇住佢<br />\n其他人就負責玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:我得20歲"},{"pid":"83fc396fd0967972ec916b0e7fd07e88e07b7cf7","tid":252204,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"公屋定私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c47f2ecb4fb355bacb80afc323a1da53483cb34","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪預左呢十幾年都陪佢先。<br />\n想清楚啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然我現家只係諗住養 但我都已經從各方面思考過 又假設過 覺得應付得黎 所以先真係話想養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最緊要都係家人贊成 家人允許同中意既話 汪汪先可以接受更多既愛 幸福快樂咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df461895475d64ce7a501ac1852b9856b7ae3649","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得你呀媽反對都好正常<br />\n因為養狗真係會好麻煩同會好臭<br />\n如果你係可以自己全部負責晒關於養狗既野<br />\n包括每日既屎屎尿尿 帶佢出街 沖涼 餵佢食野<br />\n同埋如果你唔係屋企 EG去左旅行 咁你會放棄去旅行定交底隻狗比你屋企人湊??<br />\n老左可能會失禁 到時你可能每日返到屋企成地都係尿同屎<br />\n當然呢D例子可能係太極端 但真係要諗<br />\n<br />\n一個屋企養狗真係唔只係一個人既事 係會影響晒全屋企<br />\n如果你有信心養狗唔會影響到你家人 我相信佢地都唔會阻止</blockquote><br />\n巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以現家媽咪唔say yes 我都say唔到yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c98f456a62b42e411f672e639f58afc90bc03b","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母唔鐘意狗真係唔好養，又多說話比你聽，又會瘋狂用漂白水拖地消毒（對狗唔好），會攪到家無寧日。（朋友個案）<br />\n<br />\n利申：老母最錫隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有諗過 如果屋企嘈交太大聲 汪汪可能會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a596a4ea19a501f1847ee883393361a1910809","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n岩 我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係唔係你自己照顧哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係既真係好on 9</blockquote><br />\n打針 糧 用品都係我自己搞掂<br />\n我係屋企就我照顧<br />\n我唔係度就我啊媽睇住佢<br />\n其他人就負責玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:我得20歲</blockquote><br />\n我媽比較極端 博唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efdf152703f8d9f07e9674828c0beec4b48d5de","tid":252204,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"我當年都係玩先斬後奏<br />\n宜家我老母最錫隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4305e71e24575100c3b41bad1a85ef49da0d2e","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我當年都係玩先斬後奏<br />\n宜家我老母最錫隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n潔癖好阻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e61373014ca375801f77d9e78a25eab5b7422c","tid":252204,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:21:36.000Z","msg":"我驚到時你老母當隻狗仔咁錫咋<br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人"},{"pid":"24df79543dfcde7f2e95f389f9f2e0731c175d57","tid":252204,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我驚到時你老母當隻狗仔咁錫咋<br />\n<br />\n利申 過來人</blockquote><br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一開始都話佢甩毛勁呀乜都講一餐 但之後當佢寶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fd9f1de434cb054a6e8806bec79a05d1fde599","tid":252204,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB