62773c806cc73204.jpg&h=d8ea1f04&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻狗個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e2a7a917d584e7df6a020f912c810f7cac337d","tid":252204,"uid":85186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T20:15:00.000Z","msg":"帶埋屋企人去中心過一日 自然會改觀"},{"pid":"c75d27c5ddac5987e2705142c76e8fe6d31a84e3","tid":252204,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"你養啲無咁重狗味又少甩毛嘅狗囉<br />\n我媽媽都怕 佢初初都唔畀我養<br />\n而且佢份人唔鍾意小動物<br />\n而家錫隻狗多過錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我養Poodle 係就係要日日梳毛<br />\n但真係無味 唔甩毛 污唔污糟睇你點打理"},{"pid":"4a8f17e56b4c7c51f5443e4934e2d6e7c5af1957","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你養啲無咁重狗味又少甩毛嘅狗囉<br />\n我媽媽都怕 佢初初都唔畀我養<br />\n而且佢份人唔鍾意小動物<br />\n而家錫隻狗多過錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我養Poodle 係就係要日日梳毛<br />\n但真係無味 唔甩毛 污唔污糟睇你點打理</blockquote><br />\n我想養bichon啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bichon比poodle仲多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實啲汪汪氣味係咪一開始新入屋點都有啲味 之後就關你養得乾唔乾淨事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3120c98151158e1ec5f4b227002d799c0abe4160","tid":252204,"uid":99359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你養啲無咁重狗味又少甩毛嘅狗囉<br />\n我媽媽都怕 佢初初都唔畀我養<br />\n而且佢份人唔鍾意小動物<br />\n而家錫隻狗多過錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我養Poodle 係就係要日日梳毛<br />\n但真係無味 唔甩毛 污唔污糟睇你點打理</blockquote><br />\n我想養bichon啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bichon比poodle仲多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 