/blockquote><br />\n唔好啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔一定得  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果樓豬媽媽堅決反對<br />\n最後都係害左隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，有啲媽媽性格係好硬頸<br />\n夾硬嚟只會傷感情又害埋隻狗</blockquote><br />\n岩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我媽好硬頸的"},{"pid":"2c7b1d7a4731c327bfa0c0c464d026d7e17132d7","tid":252204,"uid":22696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔洗怕 我買左返屋企 老母日日自動幫佢執屎倒尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁老媽有冇成日鬧你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始會講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢佢會中意同隻狗玩就無野"},{"pid":"95dc81d3b122201359edf1c44043550892a751b0","tid":252204,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔洗怕 我買左返屋企 老母日日自動幫佢執屎倒尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁老媽有冇成日鬧你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始會講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢佢會中意同隻狗玩就無野</blockquote><br />\n岩 朝頭早就嫌棄，之後食野就比佢食先，佢食緊又再比佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我控制唔到，然後入門口即刻同佢玩陣先。"},{"pid":"9c1967e1d8d7b666f299126146af61949ff71388","tid":252204,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你養啲無咁重狗味又少甩毛嘅狗囉<br />\n我媽媽都怕 佢初初都唔畀我養<br />\n而且佢份人唔鍾意小動物<br />\n而家錫隻狗多過錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我養Poodle 係就係要日日梳毛<br />\n但真係無味 唔甩毛 污唔污糟睇你點打理</blockquote><br />\n我想養bichon啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bichon比poodle仲多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實啲汪汪氣味係咪一開始新入屋點都有啲味 之後就關你養得乾唔乾淨事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你打理得企企理理，自然會乾淨啦，但Poodle本身無咩味，甩毛唔勁，呢個都係我揀佢嘅原因之一"},{"pid":"2bf1726a815709683f935ba41de13998261f5ffc","tid":252204,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你養啲無咁重狗味又少甩毛嘅狗囉<br />\n我媽媽都怕 佢初初都唔畀我養<br />\n而且佢份人唔鍾意小動物<br />\n而家錫隻狗多過錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我養Poodle 係就係要日日梳毛<br />\n但真係無味 唔甩毛 污唔污糟睇你點打理</blockquote><br />\n我想養bichon啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bichon比poodle仲多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實啲汪汪氣味係咪一開始新入屋點都有啲味 之後就關你養得乾唔乾淨事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你媽媽本身反對？咁最後點成功養到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我答應佢，養咗狗之後會做家務，自己打理返隻狗，照顧好佢，唔會煩到佢。結果？而家佢好錫隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959f8f90d8aa3edbc5140e9601c73c4a5caf3a0c","tid":252204,"uid":32976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"我隻狗岩岩走左。<br />\n<br />\n我只可以跟你說,如果你好愛狗。<br />\n你將來一定會面對佢要走既決定。<br />\n你問我，如果可以再選擇唔養狗定要睇住佢走。<br />\n<br />\n我一定會選前者⋯"},{"pid":"255a59cfca26cc0d98ecaaccdc25595895170b2a","tid":252204,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"教你先斬後奏嗰啲全部都係自私仆街黎<br />\n養一隻狗/貓=屋企多個成員<br />\n你屋企未有共識就養只會害左隻寵物<br />\n同埋希望你唔係玩玩吓"},{"pid":"160939f5ee8b9402cc28d191a0eaffe86a2d6a14","tid":252204,"uid":100908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"有朋友既男友送左隻狗俾佢，佢老母初初好反對。<br />\n朋友為左唔放棄隻狗自己搬出去租樓住，然後逢假期返屋企食飯先帶隻狗一齊返去，一年後左右佢老母終於接受隻狗，於是同隻狗一齊搬返去住，依家個老母都係錫隻狗多過佢。<br />\n事在人為，有心總有方法，不過情況唔同唔建議你夾硬養。"},{"pid":"179725a8073829a26e1c860c218f8626a6087b2f","tid":252204,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻狗岩岩走左。<br />\n<br />\n我只可以跟你說,如果你好愛狗。<br />\n你將來一定會面對佢要走既決定。<br />\n你問我，如果可以再選擇唔養狗定要睇住佢走。<br />\n<br />\n我一定會選前者⋯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但至少過程幸福，不是嗎？<br />\n我相信你隻狗都會覺得好幸運有個咁愛自己嘅主人。<br />\n我試過幻想隻狗走咗，會好傷心，好想喊，但同時我都會諗，我係個愛狗嘅人，我想將呢份幸福繼續帶畀其他狗，令佢哋有個家，我相信我隻狗都會希望我咁做。"},{"pid":"f7e4159fd0221b9086ccb34e12ebd0eb90ecbc55","tid":252204,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"有哮喘<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15eb60cfed62f1b1a549024b8d0a912b71caab59","tid":252204,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前斬後奏就得 養養就唔反對 唔好諗咁多</blockquote><br />\n棄狗就係呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f71f13f5a716013310d8674a7f4494f8e44ded","tid":252204,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:10:40.000Z","msg":"狗麻煩之處係會吠同要帶落街 , 所以我寧願養貓"}]}